|---------------|----------|------------------|------------------|
| {type} | {count} | {max_severity} | ${category_eal_ml} |
{...repeat for each category...}
| **TOTAL** | **{total_count}** | **â€”** | **${total_eal_ml}** |

## Remediation Guide
